{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14749/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14749"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:47:49"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Two seamstresses hellp woman try on dress while man and woman watch"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14749","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14749"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1/2e479e2a-bc7a-4ba8-8f3a-b2a9c70551cd","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T19:03:32.000Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma herself resembles Reynolds’s <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW177151699 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-12821.html\"><u>vision of his mother</u></a>, looming in the background like a ghost. Her position in the House of Woodcock has shifted as she exercises greater control in her relationship with Reynolds than at its inception. Here, Reynolds is seated rather than actively engaging in the fitting as he’s been <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW177151699 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-00749.html\"><u>seen doing before</u></a>. His power has fallen.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1174.1635151273874,243.9082404458599,156.91928742038203,428.51811305732485"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1/23cf7cf1-1ca6-456f-984f-9aac9ce07eea","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T19:04:08.685Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>This latest green dress, which doesn’t seem to excite Reynolds any, echoes the dresses worn by both <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW265353925 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-04039.html\"><u>Alma</u></a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW265353925 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-05505.html\"><u>Barbara Rose,</u></a> as well as <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW265353925 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-15324.html\"><u>Alma’s green sweater</u></a> in the climactic poisoning scene. This color, associated with nature, suggests Alma has influenced and negatively altered Reynolds’s mood. It may likewise be tied to the vomit that Reynolds emits after Alma’s poisonings.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14749/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:561.4520302547758,349.45163216560525,345.8076234076434,708.387241242038"}}}]}]}]}